Supporters the opposition run away from teargas on November 28, 2017 during demonstrations at Umoja suburb of capital Nairobi, after police denied permission for main opposition, National Super Alliance (NASA) leader to hold a rally concurrently with the inauguration of Kenyan President. (AFP) 
